'''亞美尼亞控制的納戈爾諾－卡拉巴赫周邊地區'''是[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]法理上的領土，位于[[納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫自治州|納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫自治州]]周圍，自[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]结束至[[2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]前，这些地区一直由[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]扶持的[[阿尔察赫共和国|阿尔察赫共和国]]军队控制<ref>{{Cite web|title=Сергей Маркедонов: Нужны ли российские миротворцы в Нагорном Карабахе|url=https://polit.ru/article/2006/06/02/nkr/|accessdate=2020-11-13|date=2006-06-02|publisher=ПОЛИТ.РУ|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113111012/https://polit.ru/article/2006/06/02/nkr/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=GENERAL|url=https://www.hrw.org/reports/1995/communal/|accessdate=2020-11-13|work=www.hrw.org|quote="By early 1992 full-scale fighting broke out between Nagorno-Karabakh Armenians and Azerbaijani authorities." "...Karabakh Armenian forces -often with the support of forces from the Republic of Armenia- conducted large-scale operations..." "Because 1993 witnessed unrelenting Karabakh Armenian offensives against the Azerbaijani provinces surrounding Nagorno-Karabakh..." "Since late 1993, the conflict has also clearly become internationalized: in addition to Azerbaijani and Karabakh Armenian forces, troops from the Republic of Armenia participate on the Karabakh side in fighting inside Azerbaijan and in Nagorno-Karabakh."|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172503/https://www.hrw.org/reports/1995/communal/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hsw|url=https://www.hrw.org/reports/1993/WR93/Hsw-07.htm|accessdate=2020-11-13|work=www.hrw.org|quote=In 1992 the conflict grew far more lethal as both sides -the Azerbaijani National Army and free-lance militias fighting along with it, and ethnic Armenians and mercenaries fighting in the Popular Liberation Army of Artsakh- began...|archive-date=2015-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218230025/http://www.hrw.org/reports/1993/WR93/Hsw-07.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Nagorno-Karabakh Searching for a Solution|url=http://www.usip.org/pubs/peaceworks/pwks25/forewrd25.html|accessdate=2020-11-13|publisher=U.S. Institute of Peace|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202233445/http://www.usip.org/pubs/peaceworks/pwks25/forewrd25.html|archivedate=2008-12-02|dead-url=yes|quote=Nagorno-Karabakh’s armed forces have not only fortified their region but have also occupied a large swath of surrounding Azeri territory in the hopes of linking the enclave to Armenia.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Sovereignty after Empire: Peaceworks|url=http://www.usip.org/pubs/peaceworks/pwks19/chap3_19.html|accessdate=2020-11-13|publisher=U.S. Institute of Peace|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611172201/http://www.usip.org/pubs/peaceworks/pwks19/chap3_19.html|archivedate=2009-06-11|dead-url=yes|quote=Meanwhile, the conflict over Nagorno-Karabakh was gradually transforming into a full-scale war between Azeri and Karabakh irregulars, the latter receiving support from Armenia." "Azerbaijan's objective advantage in terms of human and economic potential has so far been offset by the superior fighting skills and discipline of Nagorno-Karabakh's forces. After a series of offensives, retreats, and counteroffensives, Nagorno-Karabakh now controls a sizable portion of Azerbaijan proper (...), including the Lachin corridor.}}</ref>。阿爾察赫實際上是擁有[[國家行為|人民、領土、政府和主權]]的獨立國家，甚至擁有自己的軍隊與[[亞美尼亞德拉姆#_阿尔察赫|貨幣]]、及自行發行[[護照|護照]]與[[簽證|簽證]]。

== 歷史 ==
====2020年====

2020年9月27日的早晨，[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭|二次戰爭]]在納哥諾卡拉巴克邊界地區接觸線展開，最終該場戰爭以亞塞拜然勝利並控制[[阿塞拜疆－伊朗邊境|阿塞拜疆－伊朗邊境]]告終。<ref name="diplomatie_150720">{{cite web|title=Armenia/Azerbaijan – Border clashes between the two countries (15 Jul. 2020)|url=https://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files/armenia/news/article/armenia-azerbaijan-border-clashes-between-the-two-countries-15-jul-2020|publisher=[[法國外交部|Ministry of Europe and Foreign Affairs]] (France)|language=en|access-date=27 September 2020|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209152652/https://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files/armenia/news/article/armenia-azerbaijan-border-clashes-between-the-two-countries-15-jul-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根据[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫停火協議|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫停火協議]]結束后，亚美尼亚部队同意在2020年12月1日之前从这些地区撤出，将其归还給阿塞拜疆。作為交換條件，阿塞拜疆允许亚美尼亚人通過[[拉钦走廊|拉钦走廊]]往來於亚美尼亚本土和[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫]]之間<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/11/09/armenian-pm-announces-end-to-nagorno-karabakh-hostilities-a71997 |title=Moscow confirms peace deal signed, complete cessation of hostilities. |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=9 November 2020 |website= |publisher={{tsl|en|The Moscow Times||The Moscow Times}} |access-date= |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170217/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/11/10/russian-peacekeepers-head-to-nagorno-karabakh-after-peace-deal-a71997 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

